title: Robot 2.0
subTitle: People begin to panic after mobile phones start flying out of their hands. To bring an end to the strange phenomenon, Dr Vaseegaran is ordered to reactivate Chitti.

title: Farrey
subTitle: Brought up in an orphanage, child prodigy Niyati gets admitted into a prestigious school. Soon, surrounded by money, she gets engulfed in a cheating racket.

title: English Vinglish
subTitle: A housewife and caterer, Shashi, is usually mocked by her family for not knowing English. Her attempt to learn the language helps her rediscover herself and reassert her value as a mother and a wife.

title: Khamoshi
subTitle: A young woman, who is unable to hear and speak, attempts to save herself when a killer appears at her doorstep.

title: Bareilly Ki Barfi
subTitle: In the small-town of Bareilly, a free-spirited Bitti hates that she is being pressured into getting married. But when she reads a book that reflects her life, she sets out to find its author.

title: Dhadak
subTitle: A world of uncertainties awaits Madhu and Parthavi as their love transcends class divides and blossoms despite the fierce disapproval of their families.

title: Koyla
subTitle: Silenced by a piece of smouldering coal in childhood, Shanker endures a life of slavery until love compels him to seek his voice, freedom, and long-overdue revenge.

title: Sooryavanshi
subTitle: With the looming threat of a terrorist attack on Mumbai, ATS chief Sooryavanshi embarks on a mission to hunt for 600 kgs of missing RDX and the conspiring perpetrators.

title: Darlings
subTitle: Badru desperately wishes her abusive husband mends his ill-treatment of her. However, when her situation worsens, Badru takes matters into her own hands.

title: Bawaal
subTitle: A small-town man falls in love with the prettiest girl in town. However, he ends up marrying her in order to raise his social standing.

title: Om Bheem Bush
subTitle: Three scientists arrive at a village in search of a treasure. However, things take a turn when they explore a haunted palace and discover black magic.

title: Om Bheem Bush

title: Jihne Mera Dil Luteya
subTitle: Yuvraj and Gurnoor are friends from college but their families do not get along well. But soon hilarious chaos ensues as they both vie for the affection of the beautiful Noor.

title: Kalyug
subTitle: Kunal and Renuka's marital bliss is shattered when a group of people film and upload a video of them being intimate on an adult website. Kunal fights to take them and their illegal racket down.

subTitle: A severe water shortage pushes the residents of Upri and Bairi, two rival villages, to reconcile and face the trouble together.

title: Chakravyuh
subTitle: Kabir infiltrates a Maoist organisation to help Adil Khan, who is a decorated police officer and his friend. As he gets deeper into the organisation, Kabir starts sympathising with the group's plight and starts having second thoughts.

title: Bimbisara
subTitle: Getting betrayed by his brother, ancient evil king Bimbisara teleports to the modern-day world and traps in the mirror. Desperate to return to his empire, Bimbisara searches for the mirror to break free.

title: Saaho
subTitle: An undercover agent and his partner go after a thief who has stolen 2,000 crore rupees. Soon, they realise that the case is linked to the death of a crime lord and an emerging gang war.

title: Gadar: Ek Prem Katha
subTitle: A Sikh trucker and an aristocratic Muslim woman fall in love against the backdrop of the 1947 partition.

title: Good Newwz
subTitle: Two married couples are unsuccessful in conceiving and seek medical treatment. However, they end up in a complicated situation after their doctor makes a blunder.

title: Kho Gaye Hum Kahan
subTitle: Three friends in their twenties, Imaad, Ahana, and Neil, try to figure out life in an ever changing digital era. So, through love and heartbreak, they find support in each other.

title: Gumnaam
subTitle: An aspiring director reluctantly becomes a police officer. Soon after, he starts investigating a serial murder case wherein the killer targets teenage girls.

title: Gumnaam

title: Virgin Bhanupriya
subTitle: Bhanupriya, a conservative woman, wants to lose her virginity. Although a fortune teller warns her of it being an impossible feat, she is determined to achieve her goal.

title: Jawaani Jaaneman
subTitle: Jazz, a 40-year-old man, leads a frivolous casanova lifestyle in London. However, when Tia, a young woman claiming to be his daughter, enters his life, he decides to mend his ways.

title: Fukrey 3
subTitle: The Fukras plan to take over Delhi and run for city elections. However, they have no money, so they take on an international job to make a quick buck, which changes their lives forever.

title: Bhaagamathie
subTitle: Chanchala, an IAS officer, is imprisoned in a haunted house for interrogation. However, things take an unexpected turn when she gets possessed by a spirit.

title: Gangubai Kathiawadi
subTitle: A woman is forced to abandon her Bollywood dreams after her boyfriend sells her to a brothel. As time passes, she builds strong connections in the criminal underworld and rises to power.

title: Holiday: A Soldier Is Never off Duty
subTitle: An army intelligence officer arrives in Mumbai to spend the holiday with his family. However, he must switch back to work mode after a bomb rips through the heart of the city.

title: Madgaon Express
subTitle: Childhood friends Dodo, Ayush, and Pinku embark on a trip to Goa that goes completely off-track due to a sequence of terrible decisions.

title: Sirivennela
subTitle: A paranormal investigator encounters an enraged poltergeist, the spirit of a young child burdened by a shadowy and tragic history.
